296
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:33,369
to see the hair falling away from the beautiful
moon-like face... of Nitāi... Nimaī Paṇḍit.

297
00:36:33,369 --> 00:36:41,390
And, that barber, He swears... he'll... he
